    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once a haven for entertainment business and beauty industry, the COSMIC facility on a remote tropical island becomes the center of a deadly biological incident. A mysterious outbreak has twisted the living and the dead into monstrous plant-zombie hybrids that prey on living flesh. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped in the heart of the facility, an up-and-coming model, Nate, searches for a way out while fighting back against the horrors that stalk on every corridors. But, as he ventures deeper into the beauty company's dark secrets, he begins to uncover the sinister plot that threatens the very existence of humanity... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unravel the Mystery </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Surrounded by danger from all sides, the model desperately search for a way out while piecing together the puzzles of the outbreak: Is the incident contained within the facility? Did anyone else survive? Why is all of this happening? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/9c963215142fb1af09acd0a8202d0d53.poster.avif?t=1749710503\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/9c963215142fb1af09acd0a8202d0d53.webm?t=1749710503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/9c963215142fb1af09acd0a8202d0d53.mp4?t=1749710503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Compelling Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/2cdee870f269eb1d4ff91cfd41a0d8f7.poster.avif?t=1749710503\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/2cdee870f269eb1d4ff91cfd41a0d8f7.webm?t=1749710503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/2cdee870f269eb1d4ff91cfd41a0d8f7.mp4?t=1749710503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face the early stage of the Outbreak and discover the dark agenda of the Beauty Company behind all of this Nightmare. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the Facility</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/b7fe58c4dbef4c1002d202d2743ac23e.poster.avif?t=1749710503\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/b7fe58c4dbef4c1002d202d2743ac23e.webm?t=1749710503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/b7fe58c4dbef4c1002d202d2743ac23e.mp4?t=1749710503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden secrets and clues for the Outbreak's truth as you navigate various atmospheric Environments. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intense Survival Horror Gameplay<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/b49ff1f6f53f6799f015a24488d37085.poster.avif?t=1749710503\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/b49ff1f6f53f6799f015a24488d37085.webm?t=1749710503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/b49ff1f6f53f6799f015a24488d37085.mp4?t=1749710503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight or Flee to survive against the hordes of Plant-Infested Creatures. Use your wits and resources to outsmart the monsters. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Resource Management</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/3e67a391f828dbe17c9589a3bdeee18b.poster.avif?t=1749710503\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/3e67a391f828dbe17c9589a3bdeee18b.webm?t=1749710503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145850/extras/3e67a391f828dbe17c9589a3bdeee18b.mp4?t=1749710503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision you take will be vital to your survival, as well as strategically manage your Inventory, and search the facility for essential supplies.</p>",
